title: How to Middle Part | AXE |  Instagroom
description:
This is how Joe styles his middle part. He is a little quiet, so he lets his hair do the talking.  

THE TOOLS:
Axe Urban Messy Look Flexible Paste 

THE STEPS:
1. Rub paste into palms
2. Rake roughly
3. Part in the middle

transcripts: People know me for my hair. I take the paste. Rub it into my palms. Bend my head downwards. Roughly drag my fingers through my hair and make sure I get all the hair on the right sides. I think there is elegance in simplicity.
